center.pre:
dhtarra uvca .
dharmaketre kuruketre samavet yuyutsava .
mmak pavcaiva kimakurvata sajaya ||1-1||
center.p: 1.1. Dhrtarastra said O Sanjaya, what did my sons (and others) and Pandu's sons (and others) actually do when, eager for battle, they assembled on the sacred field, the Kuruksetra (Field of the Kurus)?
